{"type": "article", "id": 25076, "title": "加入雪松木条的琴酒包装", "description": "", "date": "2016-04-07T07:11:03Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 6, "praise_count": 73, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607115614MXg6Of9pUHhqSJn4.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这瓶 Gin 装在可容纳 700 毫升的大玻璃瓶里，有着典雅的形状和亮度很高的金黄色。特别在于在酒瓶中放了一根很细的雪松木条强调酒本身的颜色和在木材中泡制的成分。雪松木是调制这款酒的配方之一，使这瓶酒拥有更细腻的口感。这瓶酒产于阿姆斯特丹，在设计上也追求简洁干净的体验，包括大的玻璃瓶和瓶身上的白色贴纸。<a href=\"http://www.vordingsgin.com/\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607115613GCPijUnrcum3N0A4.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607115613BdfInVYaxN7lPhgJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.24444444\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607115613CPjqfGOxD0wU3chL.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.62222222\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071156147bmL5EVpxGnOzDrI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.57222222\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n\n\n"}